originalText.text:
Johnny Rice is a GENIUS!

I had the most incredible photoshoot with him, hands down the best I’ve ever had.

He fostered a warm, fun, and inviting environment and went above and beyond to make sure I had a great experience.

He made me feel so comfortable in my skin, freeing me up to play, be vulnerable, and take risks.

His lighting, attention to detail, eye for angles, and out of the box creativity made my shoot above and beyond my wildest expectations.

I could not recommend him more y’all - I literally have hundreds of incredible shots to choose from and couldn’t be happier.

Thanks so much Johnny, can’t wait for our next shoot!!

originalText.text: I had a really great experience shooting with Johnny and am very pleased with the headshots I got back. He chatted with me and listened to what I was going for, and then facilitated a warm and comfortable shoot. I've had experiences getting headshots in the past that were stressful or felt rushed, but Johnny took the time to get great shots and I really appreciated his input and advice, as well as the relaxed atmosphere. I love my new headshots and can't wait to start using them. Super affordable and great quality - highly recommend!

originalText.text: If I could describe the session in one word I would say: warmth. Working with Johnny Rice has probably been the most fun that I’ve had in front of a camera since I started taking headshots 20 years ago. He will capture the image of you that you want but also the part of you that you didn’t think you needed. I believe that he will match your vibe to the best of his ability. Do yourself a favor and book a session with him.

I absolutely loved my session with Johnny! He put me at ease very quickly and made the whole experience very free and fun. He really seemed to individualize the process and made me a collaborator instead of a commodity. And ultimately, because of that, I finally have a headshot that feels like ME!
Thanks, Johnny!
